1993:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   *         due to DIR bit readonly in center aligned mode.
1994:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   *         Ex: call @ref HAL_TIM_IC_DeInit() before HAL_TIM_IC_Init()
