3025:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   *         requires a timer reset to avoid unexpected direction
3026:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   *         due to DIR bit readonly in center aligned mode.
