3031:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   * @note   When the timer instance is initialized in Encoder mode, timer
3032:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   *         channels 1 and channel 2 are reserved and cannot be used for other
3033:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   *         purpose.
