7898:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c **** /**
7899:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   * @brief  Enables or disables the TIM Capture Compare Channel x.
7900:Drivers/STM32WBxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wbxx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  TIMx to select the TIM peripheral
